Put "recipes_w_search_terms.csv" from 
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/shuyangli94/foodcom-recipes-with-search-terms-and-tags/data
 into the same folder as this program to build the database.
 Once generated, you can set the RESET_DATABASE environment variable to false to prevent database importation from running again.
 To run the flask service, run the "flask --app main run" command.   